First. Setup Anaconda environment.

Second. Setup Nox or Android emulator 

Third. Install frida-tools

Fourth. Download frida-server and move frida-server file
- adb push "frida-server*" /data/local/tmp

Fifth. exec frida-server
- chmod 777 frida-server*
- ./frida-server* &
- ps -ef | grep frida

Sixth. connect frida client & server
- frida-ps -U
